name: 凯莱布·J·菲利普斯
name_full: 凯莱布·J·菲利普斯 Caleb J. Phillips
introduction: Caleb J Phillips was born in Redding, California on April 28, 1991, to James Clement Phillips, a Business owner, and Tracey A Phillips, a home maker. At the age of seven Caleb created his first short film. From that day he knew making motion picture was his future. Caleb graduated from LAfilm school in 2014. Caleb is the owner of Trollaxx Productions and has completed three short films. Caleb has worked on several full length features.
